data.description: Wonderful opportunity to make your home in Brook Highland's Magnolia neighborhood!  Spacious home with convenience of Primary Bedroom and Garage on Main Level.  Kitchen with large island plus breakfast area.  Den with Gas Log Fireplace leads to Glass Screened Porch and Sun Deck.  Primary Bedroom connects to Porch as well.  Huge Walk In Closets Throughout.  Large Laundry Room with Utility Sink.  Three Large Bedrooms upstairs along with Plenty of Walk In Attic Storage.  You won't believe the amount of space downstairs - so many possibilities!  Mature landscaping surrounding the home.  Proximity to the many shops/restaurants/services of Highway 280.  Property lovingly maintained by Seller - Ready for updates and new owners for its next chapter!
